info.description: # Rug Universal library for fetching Stock and ETF data from the internet - mostly unofficial APIs - no limits, more free data. (for Cryptocurrency alternative see [karpet](https://github.com/im-n1/karpet)) * [PyPI](https://pypi.org/project/rug/) * [documentation](https://rug.readthedocs.io/en/latest/) ![Documentation Status](https://readthedocs.org/projects/rug/badge/?version=latest) ## Changelog [changelog](./CHANGELOG.md)
info.name: rug
info.summary: Library for fetching various stock data from the internet (official and unofficial APIs).
